(1, 7, 'UP govt exempts interest on amount payable by industrial', 'UP govt exempts interest on amount payable by industrial', '2020-04-22 09:09:03', 'PUBLISH', 'PUBLIC', NULL, '<ul style=\"background: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #1e1e1e; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"background: transparent; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">In a major relief to all industrial and commercial institutions during COVID-19 lockdown, the Uttar Pradesh government has decided to exempt interest on the amount payable by these establishments under all heads from March 22 till June 30, 2020.</li>\r\n<li style=\"background: transparent; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The lockdown implemented for the prevention of coronavirus pandemic has resulted in the temporary closure of industrial, commercial and institutional units located all over the world, India and the state.</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', 5);
