(176, 6, 'This is the perfect time to start making money from blogging. Don\'t miss once in a lifetime opportunity.', 'This is not 2010 where people will only rely on WordPress or create our own blogging website and end up expending way higher than we would potentially earn. This is 2020 we have a lot of different ways to earn through blogs. ', '2020-07-01 10:15:36', 'PUBLISH', 'PUBLIC', '2020-07-01 10:25:46', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 30pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is the perfect time to start making money from blogging.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 30pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Don\'t miss once in a lifetime opportunity.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 30pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 624px; height: 365px;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-dbde24d5-7fff-09d6-d671-724c3faea5f4\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 30pt; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 624px; height: 365px;\"><img style=\"margin-top: 0px; float: left;\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/64SLqpIIJZxOAoRGAoGynzfd29La8XzhpQarNXbPQ1l_zP5FajokZi7Xu8LDWfcPmGHUSc4SXTgMcRim-orDwotd_1ywPNLbHOUeNEA0nZMLqRfUpKXiAg1pRpjsYN_PGVVfjl7z\" width=\"624\" height=\"365\" /></span></span></span><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Some might argue about the thoughts but it all depends on the perspective. The only reason I specifically mentioned to start blogging is humanity does not need lamborghinis or ferraris lifestyle, they need some sustainability to pay their bills. Some might need to pay rent, some might need money to pay educational fees. </span></p>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></h1>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We need some realistic approach in our life.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is the time people don\'t like to read about how to get a millionaire or any fake gurus showing 1000% increase in money from the stock market. This is a real pandemic and we need some security of income out of it. Many peoples have lost their jobs and may have insecurity about them, so why not start writing about something we love and start getting some money which would actually help us to pay our bills.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is 2020 and we need to empower ourselves:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is not 2010 where people will only rely on wordpress or create our own blogging website and end up expensening way higher than we would potentially earn. This is 2020 we have a lot of different ways to earn through blogs.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The very important departments in any company which sells their products or services is the writeup department. All the things depend on the writing. People express their views and reviews by writing about any products or services. Nowadays we have more than 100 thousand companies trying to outreach everybody and they are specifically acting the same in the marketing departments. All of them are using bloggers to reach their customers.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Building good relationships with companies is a very long process. That\'s why I would suggest using platforms especially built for blogging.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Onveraft has all the things needed to get any blog successful. They have their affiliate program and partner program to get paid. And the most important thing which many readers don\'t like are advertisements. Onveraft is an ads free platform. Their main focus is to create a good experience for users. And I think by omitting the ads they have done their best job. You can manage every single thing from the dashboard. Best part is you get an idea for your monthly and yearly payments way ahead of time. Which makes it very easy to decide whether or not we are on our financial goals. </span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Always remember the only thing that travels time is writing.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">One best tip which we all know in writing:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The best write up is the most simple writeup with no hidden secrets is the best writing. The blogs written with less than 1000 words, good grammar and no spelling mistakes give a very good impression on the reader and you don\'t need a PhD to earn 100 thousands from blogs. You just have to start writing with clean and simple language and you\'re good to go.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Final verdict:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You can earn a good amount of money from onveraft by just being consistent. Get only 25 affiliates per 4months and 15 blogs for every 4 months. Continue this simple formula and start getting life changing results. The only thing that makes some businesses successful is they have always been consistent in their whole life. Just follow their principles and we too can bring change in our lives.</span></p>\r\n<h1><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-7fdd7927-7fff-2b12-d4d3-38a206c3192a\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', 8);
